Sistemi      |                                           |
             +-------------------------------------------+
## Summary

- Frontend User handles country selection, form filling, document upload, appointment, payment.
- Back Office reviews, approves, rejects, and manages applicant documents.
- Automation Engine handles validation, locking, and notifications.
- Consulate systems receive application data and return results.